 prix tour to japan he first arrived at the pss mutiara damansara where he spent about  minutes interacting with the customers following this he arrived at the pss taman tun dr ismail where he was surrounded by fans the moment he stepped inone of the customers syed hashim omar aljunid said “i was really surprised it was definitely a good kind of surprise – to have a formula one world championship driver fuel up my car for me it is a big honour”another unsuspecting customer mohd arif abu bakar was equally surprised “i just bought my brand new car and the petronas station was my first stop to tankup with petronas primax  xtra i really did not expect to see a formula one driver here what more to tank up my new car it was definitely a double joy for me – a day that i will cherish for a long time”indeed at petronas service stations it is more than just fuelling vehicles it is a onestop centre that comes with shopping banking dining ongoing rewards and now with a possibility of having a formula one driver fuel up for you moving forward pdb is committed to bring more such unique fuelling experiences to its valued customersto know what is coming up next logon to wwwmymesracommy or join us as a fan at wwwfacebookcompetronasbrandsabout petronas dagangan berhadpetronas dagangan berhad is the principal domestic marketing arm of petroliam nasional berhad petronas the national oil company which holds  of its equity the company markets a wide range of high quality petroleum products including motor gasoline aviation fuel kerosene diesel fuel oil bunker fuel lubricants liquefied petroleum gas lpg and asphalt in malaysia for media enquiries please contact petronas dagangan berhadizrin muhayi mstel         –  fax        –  email    izrinmpetronascommy or perspective strategies sdn bhdanupama arvind mstel         –  fax        –  email    anupamaarvindperspectivecommy lim hwee nee mstel         –  fax        –  email    limhweeneeperspectivecommy petronas brands ·  · petronas xtra cha