with valuable feedback on our products and services” he added throughout the race paul tan juliana and ean took to facebook twitter and blogs to call for support what started as a close competition soon saw paul tan leading the race towards the end thanks to his large group of ‘motoring’ fans who diligently ‘pumped’ his virtual car with petronas primax  xtra paul tan triumphed with close to  while juliana followed closely behind with  supporters  in the presence of enthusiastic party revelers izuddin presented the winner’s trophy to paul tan and a token of appreciation consisting of petronas primax  xtra merchandises petronas gift card and formula one touch n’ go card both juliana and ean were also presented with trophies and tokens of appreciation elaborating further on what is in store for its customers izuddin said “we are committed to introduce products which are as innovative as our primax  xtra fuel if not more we will also continue to roll out a variety of exciting contests with more great prizes and rewards in the future” since the launch on  april  petronas primax  xtra has lived up to its association to formula ™ technology by delivering superior power coupled with more kilometre per litre visibly enjoying each moment of the party and his win the prominent blogger said “the petronas primax  xtra race has been great fun and i’m indeed delighted to be part of this race i guess there is no need for me to elaborate on the tremendous support and response received from the fans throughout the race” guests were treated to a scrumptious dinner laidout for the crowd followed by exciting trivia challenges and racing games conducted on playstations and ipads befitting the formula oneinspired theme of the petronas primax  xtra race appreciation party    for more exciting events logon to wwwfacebookcompetronasbrands or wwwmymesracommy  petronas brands ·  · petronas dagangan rewards  lucky customers kuala lumpur  june  – as part of its ongoing commitment to recognise an