nience when fuelling up their vehicles knowing that a wide range of services and offerings are available within our onestop centre” “moving forward we will continue to offer more rewardbased programmes to enable everyone to enjoy the privileges of being a petronas customer” he added  apart from rewarding their loyal customers petronas the road to rewards – kedai mesra also aimed at increasing the awareness of the convenience offered at petronas stations customers can shop at its kedai mesra as well as enjoy the ease of using other services available there including atms touch n go epay bill payment and even purchasing bus tickets quick serve restaurants and other refreshments are also available at selected stations moreover earlier this year pdb organised the road to rewards ‘ride the rm million wave’ campaign that rewarded rm million worth of prizes to its loyal customers over and above this the company also held the petronas fuelup promotion recently during which winners were presented with a total of  apple ipads enjoying the festivities at the event grand prize winner nurzila binti yusuf from kedah appeared delighted at her lucky win “even on days when i don’t fuel up my car i would still stop by at petronas stations to do my banking and stock up some snacks now on top of that i won such great prizes just by shopping at kedai mesra who doesn’t love to get paid for shopping” she beamed also visibility elated at his good fortune was the second prize winner mohd shazwan hafiz bin mohd shukri a student of universiti teknologi mara uitm remarked that he could now fulfil his long time wish of taking his parents on a holiday tucking into the scrumptious lunch laid out for the winners and guests hafiz said “it’s been awhile since we had a family holiday together the travel voucher will definitely come in handy this vacation will also be a nice time for me to start on my photography hobby now that i have a good camera to snap around with”   the participating brands in th