or quality and performance at pdb we firmly believe in going all the way to bring the very best of our products and services to our customers the primax  xtra is a testimony of our commitment to continuously invest in developing innovative products that meet and exceed our customers’ expectations the recent launch of the primax  xtra showcases the importance of continuing research and improvement to the primax line of products in growing our retail business as we believe that growth cannot only be in terms of the number of petronas service stations we have but also in continuously improving the quality of our fuel we have a fullfledged petronas fuel technician team working with our fuel technology partners to continuously innovate and enhance our product offerings we are excited to bring the f technology to the road and share it with all our customers this is part of pdb’s journey to consistently push the bar on technology to establish a new industrywide benchmark extensive tests have been carried out on the fuel in laboratories and we have carried out road test through our ‘experience to believe’ privileged trial and the feedback that we have received indicated that the fuel performed better as compared to their current fuel for  of the participants this feedback coupled with the positive results from independent test centres at milbrook and tickford in the uk has given us the confidence that we certainly have a winning product at hand moreover the launch of “all the way” is a clear testimony of pdb’s consistent and continuous commitment in developing products and services that exceed consumer and industry expectations the new primax  xtra which is inspired by f technology is one of such efforts to lead the market through innovation as proven by our consistent track record all through these years pdb is committed to go ‘all the way’ to ensure that petronas remains as the brand of st choice for malaysians i’m pleased to inform that you can now join us in this exciting journey on petronasbrands facebook and onyoutube as we go all the way for you amir hamzah azizanmanaging directorchief executive officerpetronas dagangan berhad petronas brands ·  · petronas formula one contests changes on requirements please click here for more detailshi all we have received some feedback on the contest and made some changes on requirements effective now you have to submit a photo of your formula one driving expression and write a creative caption with these three words “primax” “formula one” and “power” instead of “primax” “f” and “power” for those who have submitted previously you don’⋯⋯t have to make any changes for more details please view the petronas formula one tab under our profile picturewhat are you waiting for hurry and join the contest now to stand a chance to win a pair of “diamond” tickets to watch formula one race at sepang  special garage tour  rain concert exclusively for petronasbrands facebook fans petronas brands ·  · aspiring chefs from leading universities whip up delicacies to win cash prizes six universities showcased their team’s culinary skills in the inaugural gas petronas battle of the chefs cooking competition and went home with more than rm worth of cash and prizes the cooking competition was held on  february  at sstwo mall in petaling jaya it was a gastronomical delight with colourful ingredients and aromatic fla⋯⋯vours of herbs and spices concocted to create dishes that tantalises the taste bud the clanking sounds of pots and pans and encouraging cheers from friends and supporters filled the sstwo mall courtyard as the teams battle it out to be dubbed winner of the gas petronas battle of the chefs cooking competition the six universities that took part were berjaya university college of hospitality universiti teknologi mara uitm university tun abdul razak universiti putra malaysia upm advanced management  technology centre ptpl and food institute of malaysia each team comprised three apprentice chefs who were tasked to present their dishes that consisted of an appetizer a main course and a dessert all to be prepared and plated within two hours judging was based on innovation taste presentation timeliness and hygiene  the panel of judges were industry’s ‘otai’ – chef johari edrus former president of chef association of malaysia and chef jasman saidin former corporate executive chef of carnival cruise liners chef zamzani abdul wahab malaysia’s celebrity chef who is popularly known as chef zam provided inspiration and words of encouragement to the contestants the first prize winner went home with rm cash prize second prize with rm cash prize and third prize with rm cash prize all three winning teams also received a challenge trophy exclusive gas petronas merchandises and  cylinders of kg gas petronas cooking gas each over and above this three consolation prizes that consisted of trophies merchandises and exclusive gas petronas products were also awarded the general manager of pdb’s lpg liquefied petroleum gas business zubair abdul razak  said “as a responsible malaysian company petronas dagangan recognises the importance of playing our part in fostering the development of the local culinary and hospitality industry the gas petronas battle of the chefs is one of the platforms for us to expose young chefs to competition and to give them an opportunity to further improve the malaysian hospitality and foodservices standards” we hope this event will motivate our young talents to challenge themselves and craft even better culinary creations establishing higher benchmarks for other undergraduates to follow not only in the country but in this region as well given that malaysia is striving to become an education hub for this region he said list of winners st prizefood institute of malaysia fimnurul azwa ammeran noor hidayah aris mohd zulkhairi zainal ibidin nd prizeadvanced management and technology centre ptpl rd prizeberjaya university college of hospitality consolation prizeuniversi